OL,5,G0105 Night Coppers
OL,6,     FOn the beat with the cops who
OL,7,     Fpolice Brighton's hectic nightlife
OL,8,     Fscene. Rookies Matt and Will
OL,9,     Faccidentally stop an ex-police
OL,10,     F'guvnor'. Steve spots two legs
OL,11,     Fsticking out of a bush.
OL,12,G0210 Emergency Helicopter Medics
